  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      504.52,
      533.92,
      563.47
    ],
    "text": "Due to the influence of the above system, Showers or thundershowers will occur at times and cloudy skies are expected in Western, Sabaragamuwa, Central, North-western and Northern provinces and in Galle and Matara districts.",
